Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.38,0:00:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know there's an awesome\Ntreasure at the end of this sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And whoever gets it can be King\Nof the Pirates! Isn't that exciting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unheard-of adventures are waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage! Let that shred of courage grow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.26,0:00:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The horizons everyone\Ndreamed of were separate at first
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now they can be seen\Nthrough a single telescope
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bitter compass of destiny\Nis leading your heart astray
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so turn the wheel in the other direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:01:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.13,0:01:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toss aside your bonds and your past
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can surely smile despite that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tears shed trying to achieve\Nyour dreams aren't for naught
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.86,0:01:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precious in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.26,0:01:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.21,0:01:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji and Usopp snuck aboard\Nthe Ark Maxim to rescue Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.18,0:01:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they've been aware\Nof us for a long while now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.12,0:01:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They know?! What're we gonna do?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in worrying about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.86,0:02:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll split up inside and\Nhead straight for the deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.86,0:02:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san is there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.57,0:02:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Luffy had a gold ball\Nattached to his arm by Eneru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and was thrown from the Maxim\Ninto the ruins of Shandora,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he got back up to settle the score.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.18,0:02:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright... Dammit!\NI can't get this gold ball off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.51,0:02:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call it that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp saved Nami in the nick of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.26,0:02:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but unable to stand up to Eneru's power,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.26,0:02:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they found themselves\Ntrapped in a corner, when...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,El...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sanji-kun!\N--Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Thor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:03:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just about to ask... for a light...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Capriccio for Despair-- Looming\NDestruction of the Sky Islands!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.86,0:03:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to pay... you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... You'll pay for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing\Ninside the ship just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.61,0:03:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! You've got some nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gears have gone awry... I must fix it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.83,0:04:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! Nami fell safely\Ninto some Island Clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So high up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not the jungle, not the ruins...\NFocus on falling into the Island Clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Usopp Hopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I jumped too far! I jumped too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'm falling! I'm gonna crash!\NI'm gonna crash and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.67,0:05:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes! I forgot to unhook it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp! Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice! Nami! Sounds like\Nyou're all right! That's a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:05:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Sanji-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.93,0:06:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry you had to get all\Ncharred like this just for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't breathe! N-Nami!\NPull me outta here, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.61,0:06:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, let's get out of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why won't you come out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna die...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you, Blue Sea man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ship is not so easily brought down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:07:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fully acquainted with\Nthis ship's drive circuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.43,0:07:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even without electric power,\Nthe wind power from the 200 Jet Dials
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.80,0:07:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gathered from my homeland of Birka...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will keep the ship afloat for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you feeble beings try...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.12,0:07:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this land will meet its end!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! That huge vine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's the same one I saw in the ruins,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these are the Island Clouds up above them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruins? Oh, the city of gold?! It exists?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.88,0:07:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But all the gold is in Eneru's hands now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, Zoro and the others\Nshould be in the ruins below!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:57.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ruins of Shandora"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:07:58.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ruins of Shandora"\N"Current Location"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:07:58.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ruins of Shandora"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:07:58.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ruins of Shandora"\N"Current Location"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:07:59.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ruins of Shandora"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ruins of Shandora"\N"Current Location"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.05,0:08:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the topography or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I do know it's dangerous to stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.69,0:08:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find everyone and get off this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no safe places left here in Skypiea...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-L-Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.20,0:08:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Not that way! Left! Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:08:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! I can't turn so suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Hook!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.89,0:09:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't destroy my hometown!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.56,0:09:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giant Jack's over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but--!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.26,0:09:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit destroying stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.00,0:09:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.51,0:09:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's spewing out thunderclouds nicely...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.02,0:09:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the rat scurried off...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.92,0:09:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so restless and shrewd...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter. The festivities are soon at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.33,0:09:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin and the others are gone!\NZoro and Chopper...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:09:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Wyper and God...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the heck did they go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet they've already gone up it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.49,0:10:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Aisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.17,0:10:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way things stand, this land,\NSkypiea, will be annihilated...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.94,0:10:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky island will?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Our village, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.38,0:10:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that he'd return\Neveryone in the sky to the ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.43,0:11:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are the sky islands... going to disappear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wyper and the others are right through here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship is headed for the grand belfry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to the\Nnavigator and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:12:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're on board, could that mean they're...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.09,0:12:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it through!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Down there! Luffy! Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.47,0:12:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look after these guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.03,0:12:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... You grew hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:37.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Gyaaaaa!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.46,0:12:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that gold on your arm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,0:12:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin! The gold bell is at\Nthe top of this vine, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.47,0:12:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Eneru's after it, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the belfry does exist, it'd have to be there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:52.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Gyaaaaa!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.51,0:12:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But he's already...\N--All right, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.95,0:12:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He left...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.69,0:13:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where our\Nnavigator is? She has orange hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? If you mean Nami, she's on that ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I only hear one\Nvoice coming from the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.31,0:13:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navigator! Long-nose! Cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.35,0:13:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisa! Thank goodness! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.69,0:13:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.69,0:13:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes! A guerilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Everyone's been taken out!\NOh, if only I'd been there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Aisa! Where's Luffy?!\NWasn't he with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:14:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy just went up the vine\Nto rescue you from Eneru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Crap! We just missed each other?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.75,0:14:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He left just now. I tried to stop him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about bad timing! There's no\Ntime left! We gotta escape now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.39,0:14:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead! I'll go after him on the waver!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys just get to the Merry somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! That ship's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.58,0:14:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eneru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on, quickly! The sky is\Ngetting darker and darker!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.90,0:14:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? You need to escape at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.73,0:14:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief... Aisa still hasn't--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:15:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. She hasn't returned...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisa is a bright child. Let us have\Nfaith she is with some warriors...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.82,0:15:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't make it through this\Nwithout the ships in the dock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.59,0:15:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'd have to go around the long way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men! Use dials to create rivers\Ninside the island at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Please go to Cloud End\Nand escape to the Blue Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.24,0:15:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Eneru plans to eliminate this land!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay here, you'll all die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the last six years,\Nwhat we've known most of all
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is that Eneru has the\Npower to bring us despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:16:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that the time is imminent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point of waiting\Nfor a miracle to happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before you pray... Before you\Nturn a blind eye to reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you have to do what you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time where you could survive\Nif you lie low as a victim is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to take action!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.25,0:16:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't protect your own life\Nby blaming someone later!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.49,0:16:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now! Make the\Ndecision to leave this land!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many islanders are left?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still half of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.67,0:16:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No more baggage allowed!\NGet all the islanders out to sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.84,0:16:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.68,0:16:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! Leave the\Ntwo-billion-Extol-per-person departure fee!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazon-san! You need to escape, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Eh?\N--Hurry! To Cloud End!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.30,0:17:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Eh?\N--This land...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Eh?\N--It's about to be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then. Let us...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.56,0:18:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...begin the festivities.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamaragan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't dawdle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lightning is getting bigger and bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.69,0:19:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boats in the port have been destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the western end of the beach!\NQuickly! There are still boats there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run to the west!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.23,0:19:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly! Toss your belongings!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.28,0:19:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief! You need to get on a boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.38,0:19:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great Warrior Calgara...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.68,0:19:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please protect everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What huge lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna end up sky dust if we stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Hurry to the ship!\NI'll get Luffy and bring him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.49,0:20:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A-All right! Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.70,0:20:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta carry these guys\Nto the ship somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wyper!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.85,0:20:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness! You're conscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.78,0:20:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! We have no time! Can you walk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.79,0:20:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eneru! So you've started it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:21:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry. There's nothing we can do here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.87,0:21:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wyper...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even Luffy can deal with\Nan enemy flying into the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it in time! We gotta escape\Nbefore this land is destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.19,0:21:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An exquisite view!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.43,0:21:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't assume things are gonna\Nturn out how you want, Eneru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're feeling lonely, talk to me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.68,0:21:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gaze at the heavens\Nas you wander about
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the moon,\Nyou keep your gaze constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.66,0:22:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your deep reflection wanes\Nas you slowly disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.84,0:22:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay as you are, let those words guide you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.02,0:22:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream, you travelers who spend\Ncountless nights drifting
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.10,0:22:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you may not be able to go back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.53,0:22:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will surely start moving forward again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.41,0:23:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some 400 years ago,\Nthere was a man known as a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.05,0:23:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one believed him as he was\Nexecuted for his great lies and trickery.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.36,0:23:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the truth was still passed on\Nin the clouds high above!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.66,0:23:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.00,0:23:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Led by a Bell's Sound! Tale of\Nthe Great Warrior and the Explorer"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.47,0:23:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
